---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy Policy | Sivoro Microfluidics"
  description="Privacy policy for Sivoro Microfluidics website."
>
  <section style="padding-top:calc(64px + 4rem); padding-bottom:6rem; background:#0B0F19; min-height:80vh;">
    <div class="container-narrow">
      <div class="reveal">
        <span class="section-label">Legal</span>
        <h1 class="headline" style="font-size:2rem; margin-bottom:0.5rem;">Privacy Policy</h1>
        <p style="color:#8B95A5; font-size:0.875rem; margin:0 0 3rem;">Last updated: June 2026</p>

        <div style="color:#8B95A5; line-height:1.8; font-size:0.9375rem;">

          <h2 style="color:#F8F9FA; font-size:1.25rem; font-weight:600; margin:2.5rem 0 0.75rem;">1. Information We Collect</h2>
          <p>Sivoro Microfluidics ("Sivoro," "we," "us") operates this website as a static informational site. We may collect the following information when you contact us:</p>
          <ul style="padding-left:1.5rem; margin:0.75rem 0;">
            <li>Name and email address when you send us an inquiry</li>
            <li>Organization affiliation</li>
            <li>The content of your message</li>
          </ul>
          <p>We do not use tracking pixels, advertising networks, or behavioral analytics tools.</p>

          <h2 style="color:#F8F9FA; font-size:1.25rem; font-weight:600; margin:2.5rem 0 0.75rem;">2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
          <p>Information you provide is used solely to:</p>
          <ul style="padding-left:1.5rem; margin:0.75rem 0;">
            <li>Respond to your inquiry or request</li>
            <li>Send requested materials (e.g., pitch deck)</li>
            <li>Notify you of relevant company updates if you opt in</li>
          </ul>
          <p>We do not sell, rent, or share your personal information with third parties for marketing purposes.</p>

          <h2 style="color:#F8F9FA; font-size:1.25rem; font-weight:600; margin:2.5rem 0 0.75rem;">3. Cookies</h2>
          <p>This website does not use cookies beyond those strictly necessary for site functionality. No third-party tracking cookies are set. No consent banner is required.</p>

          <h2 style="color:#F8F9FA; font-size:1.25rem; font-weight:600; margin:2.5rem 0 0.75rem;">4. Third-Party Services</h2>
          <p>This site loads fonts from Google Fonts (fonts.googleapis.com). Google's privacy policy applies to font loading. No other third-party scripts are loaded.</p>

          <h2 style="color:#F8F9FA; font-size:1.25rem; font-weight:600; margin:2.5rem 0 0.75rem;">5. Data Retention</h2>
          <p>Email inquiries are retained for as long as necessary to fulfill the purpose of the communication, and no longer than 3 years unless required by law.</p>

          <h2 style="color:#F8F9FA; font-size:1.25rem; font-weight:600; margin:2.5rem 0 0.75rem;">6. Your Rights</h2>
          <p>You have the right to request access to, correction of, or deletion of any personal data we hold about you. To exercise these rights, contact us at <a href="mailto:hello@sivoro.bio" style="color:#00D4AA;">hello@sivoro.bio</a>.</p>

          <h2 style="color:#F8F9FA; font-size:1.25rem; font-weight:600; margin:2.5rem 0 0.75rem;">7. Contact</h2>
          <p>Privacy questions: <a href="mailto:hello@sivoro.bio" style="color:#00D4AA;">hello@sivoro.bio</a><br>Sivoro Microfluidics · Ann Arbor, Michigan</p>

        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
